WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.035 --> 00:00:04.537
This experience will be
documented by

00:00:04.570 --> 00:00:06.372
a mounted onboard camera.

00:00:06.405 --> 00:00:08.641
Total solitude.

00:00:08.674 --> 00:00:11.811
The terrible arrow injuries
I received to my left shoulder

00:00:11.844 --> 00:00:13.679
are making it
more difficult to row,

00:00:13.712 --> 00:00:16.215
but I'm not about to let that
ruin this relaxing sojourn

00:00:16.248 --> 00:00:18.117
across a peaceful bay.

00:00:18.150 --> 00:00:20.586
I took a few extra painkillers

00:00:20.619 --> 00:00:23.489
and I gotta try to limit
my range of motion.

00:00:23.522 --> 00:00:26.526
[chuckles]
[seagull caws]

00:00:26.559 --> 00:00:28.327
Let's follow that bird.

00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:30.329
I don't know if
it's the cool breeze

00:00:30.362 --> 00:00:32.498
or the sound of lapping water

00:00:32.531 --> 00:00:34.500
or the double dose of OxyContin

00:00:34.533 --> 00:00:37.537
or the crisp salt air,

00:00:37.570 --> 00:00:39.439
but I feel at peace in a way
that I haven't felt

00:00:39.472 --> 00:00:42.642
in a long, long time.

00:00:42.675 --> 00:00:47.080
Think I'm just gonna lie back
and enjoy it.

00:00:47.113 --> 00:00:50.450
(Forrest voice-over)
But perhaps I had allowed myself
to feel too peaceful.

00:00:50.483 --> 00:00:54.153
[snores]

00:00:54.186 --> 00:00:57.156
[dramatic music]

